QuestData.Title: Ascend No More!
QuestData.Description: TO STOP... THEIR... RITUALS OF ASCENSION... YOU MUST DESTROY... THE ANCIENT CONDUITS.$B$BTHEY USE... THE CONDUITS TO... SIPHON... MY ENERGIES AWAY... AND MAKE... ASCENDANTS.$B$BA FIGHT WITH... NEPTULON IS IMMINENT. THE TWILIGHT'S HAMMER... MUST BE DENIED... THESE CREATURES.
QuestData.CompletionText: I GROW WEAKER. YOU MUST DESTROY... MORE CONDUITS BEFORE... I DIE.
